# OnTrack

Meal planner & budgeter — Flask API + React SPA (migrating to FastAPI in `backend/`).

## Non-negotiable during backend migration

- **Frontend contract:** `docs/backend-migration/API_CONTRACT.md` and `frontend/src/api.js`
- **Auth response:** `{ "token": "..." }` — not `{ access_token, refresh_token }`
- **Do not modify** frontend appearance, CSS, `LanguageContext`, tour, or routing unless explicitly requested
- **Do not push to `main`** — use PR + green CI (`.github/DEPLOY.md`)
- **Never commit** `.env` or secrets

## Migration roadmap

Read `docs/backend-migration/README.md` before large backend work. One MIG task per branch.

## Stack

| Layer | Current | Target |
|-------|---------|--------|
| API | Flask `app/` | FastAPI `backend/` |
| Frontend | `frontend/` | unchanged |
| DB | Postgres, `migrations/` | same schema, new `backend/alembic/` |
